    "description": "<strong>Bad news</strong>: Earth was just hit by an asteroid.<br><strong>Good news</strong>: You survived!<br><br>As the last surviving medic, the faith of humankind lies in your hands. Or, something like that.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905040/extras/ae4cfe5cc0b7076686b47ef9a9cd4d13.avif?t=1705433357\" width=600 height=124 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Jump, double-jump, jet, dash, and fast-fall (in any order). Your jetpack has a limited range, but it resets when you land on solid ground.<br></li><li> Explore 200+ levels across 18 different planets, each with their own unique visual and musical themes.<br></li><li> Quickly retry levels when you die, thanks to a multi-checkpoint system.<br></li><li> Enjoy a variety of originally composed music. You'll rarely hear the same tune twice.<br></li><li> Pilot a submarine-like personal craft through a handful of underwater levels.<br></li><li> Fly a hoverboard on one of the planets.<br></li><li> Discover various secrets and Easter eggs scattered throughout the galaxy.<br></li><li> Jump straight into the action! There's no hand-holding, no dialog, and no long text to read. The story is implied by the environment.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905040/extras/6304c633e66031067772ac024647bf89.avif?t=1705433357\" width=600 height=124 /></span>",
